<i>BERTHA: This was much more
than just an earthquake.</i>

807
01:06:44,960 --> 01:06:46,086
What was it?

808
01:06:46,600 --> 01:06:48,011
It's a miracle.

809
01:06:48,200 --> 01:06:49,770
(GRUNTING)

810
01:06:50,280 --> 01:06:51,964
Let people believe
what they want.

811
01:06:52,080 --> 01:06:54,321
They need crap
like this to believe

812
