MAN 13 Right there!

879
01:12:47,480 --> 01:12:48,686
In the paper.

880
01:12:48,800 --> 01:12:49,801
Little Boy.

881
01:12:51,960 --> 01:12:52,961
It's Little Boy.

882
01:12:55,640 --> 01:12:56,880
