01:15:02,160 --> 01:15:05,164
The bomb may not be good
for American prisoners.

914
01:15:07,160 --> 01:15:08,730
What do you mean?

915
01:15:09,000 --> 01:15:11,526
It means that the Japanese
may try to harm your dad

916
01:15:11,600 --> 01:15:13,250
