01:19:36,800 --> 01:19:37,881
MRS. BUSBEE: How is he?

956
01:19:39,440 --> 01:19:40,441
(SIGHS)

957
01:19:41,240 --> 01:19:42,571
His heart is very weak.

958
01:19:42,680 --> 01:19:44,728
But he's gonna be okay, right?

959
01:19:51,240 --> 01:19:52,366
I don't know.

