969
01:21:20,080 --> 01:21:21,206
Nurse!

970
01:21:21,800 --> 01:21:22,847
NURSE 1: Get the doctor.

971
01:21:22,920 --> 01:21:24,126
NURSE 21 Dr. Foley!

972
01:21:25,280 --> 01:21:26,725
