973
01:21:27,960 --> 01:21:29,803
Mr. Hashimoto, can you hear me?

974
01:21:30,480 --> 01:21:32,050
Can you hear me?

975
01:21:32,120 --> 01:21:33,804
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

976
