997
01:26:11,040 --> 01:26:14,726
<i>My mother still chose to have
a memorial for him back home.</i>

998
01:26:14,800 --> 01:26:16,609
PRIEST: Let us commit
James L. Busbee's body

999
01:26:16,680 --> 01:26:18,603
