some time alone.

1033
01:32:34,120 --> 01:32:35,645
Maybe after some time.

1034
01:32:35,760 --> 01:32:37,205
You're a good man, Dr. Fox.

1035
01:32:38,440 --> 01:32:41,330
But I will always be
Mrs. James Busbee.

1036
01:32:45,240 --> 01:32:46,241
(SIGHS)

1037
01:32:46,320 --> 01:32:47,560
Come on.

1038
